message.body: I finished the video. Check it out!
Just saw it! I think it's better than the first time I watched it but I don't remember very well haha
Lol thanks. I still have yet too see woodkid sober and I keep viewing it
So everytime you see it are you drunk? Haha
Yea I just get the urge when I'm drunk I guess
So when u gonna invite me to woods?
You're welcomed anytime but you can't stay in my house :(.
Yea I know. Got hotels by u?
Not sure. I live in Morris county, so maybe you can check it out online.
To where is your roomie gonna move for work?
What do u mean?
Your roomie is going to be at NJ, right? If he's not far from here maybe you can stay with him.
who said he was movin?
Hu, I understand that when I talk to him. Nevermind.
He said that to u?
Don't remember, I guess so. I understand he will be going to NJ for a brief time or something like that. But don't pay much attention of what I say haha
Yea he gotta new job but he is just commuting
Morristown close to u?
Yeah, like 20 min aprox.
If I stayed there could u get there?
Yeah, that's the place where my friends and I usually go to bars and stuff.
but u couldn't get to Philly from there?
Nope.
4 hr train ride lol wtf...it can be done though
Haha yeah, practically you have to move to NY and take the train from there to Morristow. Realize know why I was so tired when I got to Philly? Haha
Ed would prolly drive me if u had a friend lol
What do you mean "if I have a friend"? Haha
I mean if he had someone to hang out with and a reason to go
Ah! Get it haha. He can hang out with us if he wants to haha.
Yea I'm sure he won't wanna just hang with me and u
I can introduce you to my other CS friends haha.
Yea maybe hell lemme borrow his car lol
That's an option haha
Yea I doubt he'd be down with that
But you should give it a shot.
It'd be more likely if u had a friend who could hang out
I told you I have friends here haha.
OK any that might like Ed? He likes sports and beer lol
Haha I know a couple of places with that description haha. The thing is that you should know that you're entering to the suburbs, and there isn't much to see.
I meant do any of ur friends like guys like that lol
Aaah got it. So are you hoping for a hook up for Ed? I don't think so! Hahah
Well someone to chill with at least. I'm just tryna get a ride! Ha
Yeah, I think he will get along with the guys.
Y not?
I didn't say "not".
Oh whoops
